{"tid":2077803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［勿以善小而不為］一人一個仍然為呢場運動做緊嘅野","createTime":"2020-06-24T14:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T01:48:18.000Z","uid":181549,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0de871343cd55cf327cb3972d8d48d55b46ee8","tid":2077803,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷黨鐵（寧願早啲起身行遠啲坐巴士/坐船/叫黃的因為831真係永遠無辦法原諒）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />IG/FB貼文宣（其實呢個舉動多數俾啲同路人睇 因為藍嘅已經del曬）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國際戰線twitter（初頭唔係好識玩 但係文宣組有出過教學 建議可以follow埋自己鍾意睇嘅日本明星/其他野 因為如果淨係當twitter係抗爭咁打好快你會唔玩）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得閒無事開著個youtube （你有野做 咪教到最細聲 最緊要comment, like, advisement, share)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />mark住日程表 提下同路人幾時要出席活動（多你一個好多 我地以前係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />工作方面幫手叫黃店外賣（藍同事會因為唔想煩而屈服）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屋企方面（幫全家裝哂蘋果,VPN, Youtube, Viu, HKTV apps,刪tvb,裝黃店apps教佢地用)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />節日消費（先前和你宵已經帶埋家人去 到而家買糭 月餅 全部黃色經濟圈）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捐錢俾612星火黃媒（推介HongKong FreePress 誌傳媒 其他細媒體都要大家幫幫手）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似仲有 但未諗到 大家交流下 每人盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n6✌🏻8 尖sha嘴見<br />\n7👆🏻港島見"},{"pid":"773d28dd78e9becd9369c2c90434b62dac788b99","tid":2077803,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5ULpQ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https